<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ صَلَّى اللَّهُ عَلَيْهِ وَسَلَّمَ:</span> <span class="c2">«اطْلُبُوا الْحَوَائِجَ مِنْ حِسَانِ الْوُجُوهِ»</span> ،<span class="c5"> وَذَكَرَ بَعْضُهُمْ أَنَّ قَوْلَهُ:</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>